---
description: Rules for user interface components
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use input() and output() from @angular/core
- Add the “pf-” (portfolio) prefix to all selectors
- Keep templates under 100 lines; extract subcomponents
- Use TailwindCSS for styling
- Use the DaisyUI library to customize components
- Add interactivity to elements
- Add animations to components